The &amp;quot;Primary Cooperative Agriculture and Rural Development Bank: For Tractor Purchase&amp;quot; scheme launched by the Co-operation, Food and Consumer Protection Department, Tamil Nadu, aims to provide financial assistance for acquiring tractors, covering up to 90% of the tractor&amp;#39;s cost. The interest rate ranges from 11% to 12.25%, subject to market conditions.
